🔟 Miscellaneous
FizzBuzz: check multiples of 3 & 5
Leap Year: divisible by 4 & (not 100 or divisible by 400)
Reverse Integer: modulo 10 & division
Sum Even / Odd / Natural numbers: loop or formula
•	Sum n: n*(n+1)//2
•	Sum first k even: k*(k+1)
•	Sum first k odd: k*k
